messages.messageBody:
Oh, We have a poster of Sully. Love that mountain man!!! Another is that cute
guy in Knight's Tale. Nita my oldest isn't here, so can't ask his name....we
watched that movie all winter! Ended up attending a Renaissance Faire because
of that. Boy did we get a good taste of history there. Like stepping back in
time! The food, music, all the clothes, games ,even the dialect... so cool. We
were really interested in the weapons. We have done re-enacting,
colonial/pioneer Tennessee at the time of the first Govener,1796. The kids really got into
it.
Hugs, Patti
